response.overview: Molly Gunn, the freewheeling daughter of a deceased rock legend, is forced to get a job when her manager steals her money. As nanny for precocious Ray, the oft ignored daughter of a music executive she learns what it means to be an adult while teaching Ray how to be a child.
response.tagline: They're about to teach each other how to act their age.
response.title: Uptown Girls

results.name: Molly Takes Ray To Coney Island
